@startuml
title Viaverse Taxonomy Admin / Publish — Activity Diagram
start
:Admin edits taxonomy;
:Create taxonomy draft\ncategory/tag/form;
:Define rules\nfields/risk/fees/visibility;
:Add localized labels\nslugs/icons;
:Validate tree\nno cycles/no duplicates;
if (Valid?) then (yes)
  :Run impact analysis\nsearch/forms/SEO;
  :Review/approve\ncontent ops;
  :Publish new version;
  :Invalidate caches\nclient/search/SEO;
  :Reindex affected entities;
  :Emit TaxonomyPublished;
  :Monitor quality\nmisclassification/no-result;
else (no)
  :Return to draft with errors;
endif
stop

note bottom
Taxonomy changes are versioned.
A published version must be backward-compatible with existing requests,
provider capabilities and SEO URLs or include explicit migration mapping.
end note
@enduml
